_sText:
Its a house with 2 rooms the others are locked. Each room is detailed with props they are set to prop_physics_multiplayer if your using this for a zombie map just remove the multiplayer so they are prop_physics. One of the rooms has a lock on it you can see through the window which you must shoot out to unlock the room, you can either shoot it out through the door or window. If you walk down the hall a zombie will break the wall down and chase you down the hall if he catches you, you will get mauled to death his name is bob who was made using the attacking zombie tutorial. If you use this please credit me, and if you like it please write a response here or vote for it thanks. (thanks to plasmicpie for the video)
